name: Babysitter Super Nanny Daycare
description:
Play now to take care of cute baby girl Emma waiting for you in this adorable babysitting game. Get ready to play the role of virtual nanny & babysitter with the exciting baby care challenging tasks designed to make babysitting game more fun for you. Step into a nanny shoes & perform daycare tasks with love & affection for the new born cute baby.

Features of Babysitter Super Nanny Daycare:
Cute 3D model of baby girl Emma.
Super nanny 3D model
Virtual house designed for baby caring
Adorable sound effects of baby
